Maybe today is unremarkable, 
but,
perhaps it also has pleasant sunshine;
or beautiful music which worth to share;
or some exciting moments;
or some unspeakable emotions...

Just write down every memorable moment;
write down every sentence you want to say;
To: xx

---------------------------------

TOXX is a healing diary notepad

Every meaningful fragment in life can be recorded in TOXX.
Whatever simple life records;
or something you want to tell someone but can’t speak;
TOXX can help you keep them well.

APP features:
* Simple and convenient operation, record anytime and anywhere;
* A variety of fonts are available to enrich every sentence;
* Kinds of characteristic templates, switch with mood;
* A lot of cute deco stickers, add personality embellishment;
* Cloud Storage Service is supported to save your records.

If you have any comments or suggestions,
welcome to leave a message to us in the APP [Settings]→[Feedback]
Every one of your suggestions is very precious~
You can also contact: hi-toxx@foxmail.com

TOXX is still being optimized
Thank you for your love and support


Then,
What are you going to say to me today? :)
